#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris-teachers.appdata.xml:18
msgid ""
"GCompris-teachers is a companion application for teachers to enhance their "
"use of GCompris in their classroom."
msgstr ""
"GCompris-teachers (Instructores de GCompris) es un application companion per "
"instructores per augmentar lor usage de GCompris in lor sala de classe."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.gcompris-teachers.appdata.xml:19
msgid ""
"It allows teachers to create customized datasets and receive pupils results "
"for some activities."
msgstr ""
"Il permitte que instructores crea insimul de datos personalisate e recipe "
"resultatos de alumnos per alcun activitates. "

